OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,6,Fdrizzle, especially along southern
OL,7,Fcoastal districts and hills. Becoming
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter in the afternoon.
OL,9,FVery warm and humid. Chance of
OL,10,Fisolated thunderstorms by evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud and showers clear
OL,13,Feastwards giving a dry and settled
OL,14,Fevening. Winds are light but breezy
OL,15,Falong the coast. Overnight
OL,16,Ftemperatures remaining warm and muggy.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FMostly fine with some
OL,19,Fsunshine. Turning very warm or locally
OL,20,Fhot, and feeling humid. Winds remain
OL,21,Flight and variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
